":"Try this link<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7086290e7a70bd3505c561a6130ff3aa6ec93c","tid":1474221,"uid":208075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:25:53.000Z","msg":"都係入唔到呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b25a7aff1ad60aebef9939de3e283ae353dd24","tid":1474221,"uid":139409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:26:55.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=22de8cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=22de8cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"a0566ac9426280a3bcdf34b7e4f2a840855a7b06","tid":1474221,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"有冇去咗SEHH1008?"},{"pid":"a906a12f805cee3c931f8c15f1898cdced0a9ac7","tid":1474221,"uid":208075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0566ac9426280a3bcdf34b7e4f2a840855a7b06","tid":1474221,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"有冇去咗SEHH1008?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"有呀 求問group link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3173f87fea752695315927fcc463f5f26ddbc7e9","tid":1474221,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a906a12f805cee3c931f8c15f1898cdced0a9ac7","tid":1474221,"uid":208075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0566ac9426280a3bcdf34b7e4f2a840855a7b06","tid":1474221,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"有冇去咗SEHH1008?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"有呀 求問group link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class